2\\/05\\/nam-linh-chi-han-quoc-2.jpg\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/sgshop.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/05\\/nam-linh-chi-han-quoc-2.jpg 800w, https:\\/\\/sgshop.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/05\\/nam-linh-chi-han-quoc-2-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\\/\\/sgshop.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/05\\/nam-linh-chi-han-quoc-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\\/\\/sgshop.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/05\\/nam-linh-chi-han-quoc-2-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\\/\\/sgshop.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/05\\/nam-linh-chi-han-quoc-2-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\\/\\/sgshop.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/05\\/nam-linh-chi-han-quoc-2-100x100.jpg 100w\\\" width=\\\"800\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u v\\u1ec1 n\\u1ea5m linh chi th&aacute;i l&aacute;t 500g<br \\/>\\r\\nN\\u1ea5m linh chi th&aacute;i l&aacute;t 500g l&agrave; s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1eeb H&agrave;n Qu\\u1ed1c. Ngo&agrave;i nh&acirc;n s&acirc;m, n\\u1ea5m linh chi t\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t n\\u01b0\\u1edbc n&agrave;y c\\u0169ng n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng kh&ocirc;ng k&eacute;m nh\\u1edd nh\\u1eefng t&aacute;c d\\u1ee5ng tuy\\u1ec7t v\\u1eddi m&agrave; n&oacute; mang l\\u1ea1i. Th\\u1eadm ch&iacute;, n\\u1ea5m linh chi \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x\\u1ebfp v&agrave;o lo\\u1ea1i si&ecirc;u th\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng ph\\u1ea9m h\\u01a1n c\\u1ea3 nh&acirc;n s&acirc;m, v&agrave; c&oacute; h&agrave;m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng gecmani cao h\\u01a1n nh&acirc;n s&acirc;m \\u0111\\u1ebfn 5 &ndash; 8 l\\u1ea7n.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\u0110\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th&aacute;i s\\u1eb5n v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng l&aacute;t m\\u1ecfng, c\\u1ea7m v\\u1eeba tay v&agrave; c&oacute; kh\\u1ed1i l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng 500g tr&ecirc;n m\\u1ed7i t&uacute;i, s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m gi&uacute;p b\\u1ea1n thu\\u1eadn ti\\u1ec7n trong vi\\u1ec7c ch\\u1ebf bi\\u1ebfn v&agrave; d\\u1ec5 mang theo khi c\\u1ea3 nh&agrave; \\u0111i du l\\u1ecbch. Gi&uacute;p b\\u1ea1n v\\u1eeba c&oacute; 1 chuy\\u1ebfn \\u0111i vui v\\u1ebb, v\\u1eeba gi&uacute;p n&acirc;ng cao s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe cho c\\u1ea3 gia \\u0111&igrave;nh.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>H&igrave;nh \\u1ea3nh: S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eadp tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1eeb H&agrave;n Qu\\u1ed1c<br \\/>\\r\\nTh&agrave;nh ph\\u1ea7n c&oacute; trong n\\u1ea5m linh chi th&aacute;i l&aacute;t 500g<br \\/>\\r\\nGermanium: Gi&uacute;p t\\u1ebf b&agrave;o m&aacute;u h\\u1ea5p th\\u1ee5 oxy t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n, nh\\u1edd \\u0111&oacute; c&oacute; t&aacute;c d\\u1ee5ng gi&uacute;p m&aacute;u l\\u01b0u th&ocirc;ng t\\u1ed1t v&agrave; tr&aacute;nh c&aacute;c hi\\u1ec7n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng nh\\u1ee9c \\u0111\\u1ea7u, ch&oacute;ng m\\u1eb7t v&agrave; t&igrave;nh tr\\u1ea1ng thi\\u1ebfu m&aacute;u l&ecirc;n n&atilde;o ng\\u0103n ch\\u1eb7n \\u0111\\u1ed9t qu\\u1ef5, tai bi\\u1ebfn.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Acid ganoderic: T\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c&aacute;c ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng trong c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3, l&agrave;m tr\\u1ebb h&oacute;a m&ocirc; v&agrave; t\\u1ebf b&agrave;o. T\\u1eeb \\u0111&oacute; gi&uacute;p c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n l&agrave;n da v&agrave; kh\\u1eafc ph\\u1ee5c c&aacute;c v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 g&acirc;y l&atilde;o h&oacute;a da.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Acid oleic: C&ograve;n goi l&agrave; omega 9 &ndash; m\\u1ed9t lo\\u1ea1i acid b&eacute;o d\\u1ea1ng l\\u1ecfng. Ch\\u1ea5t n&agrave;y r\\u1ea5t t\\u1ed1t cho tim m\\u1ea1ch, ki\\u1ec3m so&aacute;t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng huy\\u1ebft, ch\\u1ed1ng oxy h&oacute;a trong c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3, gi\\u1ea3m cholesterol trong m&aacute;u \\u0111&aacute;ng k\\u1ec3.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Ganoderans hay Polysaccharides: Gi&uacute;p t\\u0103ng kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng mi\\u1ec5n d\\u1ecbch trong c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3, ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u1ea1i c&aacute;c t&aacute;c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng x\\u1ea5u t\\u1eeb m&ocirc;i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i, gi\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1ed9c gan, ph&ograve;ng ch\\u1ed1ng tim m\\u1ea1ch v&agrave; c&oacute; kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng di\\u1ec7t c&aacute;c t\\u1ebf b&agrave;o ung th\\u01b0.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Adenosine: L&agrave;m \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh nh\\u1ecbp tim, c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n l\\u01b0u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng m&aacute;u \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c v\\u1eadn chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ebfn tim trong c&aacute;c x&eacute;t nghi\\u1ec7m tim g\\u1eafng s\\u1ee9c. \\u0110\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh sinh h&oacute;a trong c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c di\\u1ec5n ra b&igrave;nh th\\u01b0\\u1eddng. T\\u1eeb \\u0111&oacute; gi&uacute;p b\\u1ea1n c&oacute; m\\u1ed9t gi\\u1ea5c ng\\u1ee7 ngon v&agrave; s&acirc;u h\\u01a1n.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Beta-D-glucan: L&agrave;m gi\\u1ea3m cholesterol huy\\u1ebft thanh v&agrave; lipoprotein gan, d\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u1ebfn h\\u1ea1 th\\u1ea5p x\\u01a1 v\\u1eefa \\u0111\\u1ed9ng m\\u1ea1ch, gi\\u1ea3m nguy c\\u01a1 c&aacute;c b\\u1ec7nh tim m\\u1ea1ch nguy hi\\u1ec3m. T\\u0103ng nhu \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ru\\u1ed9t, c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n c&aacute;c v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng ti&ecirc;u h&oacute;a, l&agrave;m h\\u1ea1 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng huy\\u1ebft, gi\\u1ea3m thi\\u1ec3u c&aacute;c nguy c\\u01a1 tim m\\u1ea1ch \\u1edf b\\u1ec7nh nh&acirc;n ti\\u1ec3u \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng.<\\/p>\"},\"vi\":{\"name\":\"N\\u1ea5m linh chi th\\u00e1i l\\u00e1t H\\u00e0n Qu\\u1ed1c b\\u1ed3i b\\u1ed5 c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3\",\"keyword\":\"N\\u1ea5m linh chi th\\u00e1i l\\u00e1t H\\u00e0n Qu\\u1ed1c b\\u1ed3i b\\u1ed5 c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3\",\"description\":\"C\\u00f4ng d\\u1ee5ng: M\\u00e1t gan, \\u0111i\\u1ec1u h\\u00f2a huy\\u1ebft \\u00e1p r\\u1ea5t t\\u1ed1t, t\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe, b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 tim m\\u1ea1ch, ph\\u00f2ng ng\\u1eeba ti\\u1ec3u \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng\",\"content\":\"<h2><strong>N\\u1ea5m linh chi th&aacute;i l&aacute;t H&agrave;n Qu\\u1ed1c 500g b\\u1ed3i b\\u1ed5 c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>T\\u1eeb xa