cute;n,ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m \\u0111i\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ebfn 30% S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m gi\\u1ea3m th\\u1eddi gian n\\u1ea5u \\u0111\\u1ebfn 15%, th\\u1eddi gian n\\u1ea5u ch&aacute;o v&agrave; s&uacute;p \\u0111\\u1ebfn 40%. Th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n n\\u1ea5u ch&iacute;n nhanh nh\\u01b0ng v\\u1eabn gi\\u1eef nguy&ecirc;n m&ugrave;i v\\u1ecb, ch\\u1ea5t dinh d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng. C&oacute; ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng h\\u1eb9n gi\\u1edd ti\\u1ec7n l\\u1ee3i gi&uacute;p b\\u1ea1n c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 l&agrave;m vi\\u1ec7c kh&aacute;c ho\\u1eb7c ngh\\u0129 ng\\u01a1i th\\u01b0 gian trong khi n\\u1ed3i \\u0111ang n\\u1ea5u m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng lo th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n s\\u1ebd b\\u1ecb ch&aacute;y, kh&ocirc;ng ch&iacute;n,&hellip; N\\u1ed3i c&oacute; thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 7 l\\u1edbp \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o an to&agrave;n cho ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111a n\\u0103ng, c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 d&ugrave;ng \\u0111\\u1ec3n\\u1ea5u c\\u01a1m, ch&aacute;o, canh, h\\u1ea7m, h\\u1ea5p th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n&hellip;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>N\\u1ed3i &aacute;p su\\u1ea5t \\u0111a n\\u0103ng Asanzo PC-65AS1 c&oacute; dung t&iacute;ch 6 L, gi&uacute;p b\\u1ea1n tho\\u1ea3i m&aacute;i ch\\u1ebf bi\\u1ebfn c&aacute;c m&oacute;n \\u0103n ngon cho gia \\u0111&igrave;nh. L&ograve;ng n\\u1ed3i b\\u1eb1ng h\\u1ee3p kim nh&ocirc;m tr&aacute;ng men ch\\u1ed1ng d&iacute;nh, v\\u1ecf n\\u1ed3i b\\u1eb1ng inox cao c\\u1ea5p gi&uacute;p ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng s\\u1ebd th&ecirc;m ti\\u1ec7n l\\u1ee3i, nhanh ch&oacute;ng khi ch\\u1ebf bi\\u1ebfn c&aacute;c m&oacute;n \\u0103n th\\u01a1m ngon cho gia \\u0111&igrave;nh. S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m c&oacute; nhi\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng nh\\u01b0: n\\u1ea5u c\\u01a1m, n\\u1ea5u ch&aacute;o, n\\u1ea5u canh, n\\u1ea5u soup, h\\u1ea7m th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n&hellip; N\\u1ea5u th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n nhanh ch&iacute;n, gi\\u1eef nguy&ecirc;n h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v\\u1ecb, ch\\u1ea5t dinh d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng. N\\u1ed3i c&oacute; c&ocirc;ng su\\u1ea5t 1.000W v&agrave; n\\u1eafp \\u0111\\u1eady k&iacute;n, kh&iacute;t ch\\u1eb7t gi\\u1eef cho h\\u01a1i kh&ocirc;ng tho&aacute;t ra ngo&agrave;i. Nh\\u1edd v\\u1eady m&agrave; &aacute;p su\\u1ea5t v&agrave; nhi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed9 trong n\\u1ed3i t\\u0103ng cao, gi&uacute;p th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n nhanh ch&iacute;n m&agrave; v\\u1eabn gi\\u1eef \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nguy&ecirc;n v\\u1eb9n m&ugrave;i v\\u1ecb v&agrave; c&aacute;c ch\\u1ea5t dinh d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>N\\u1ed3i &aacute;p su\\u1ea5t \\u0111a n\\u0103ng Asanzo PC-65AS1 ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u nh&ocirc;m cao c\\u1ea5p, ch\\u1ed1ng d&iacute;nh. L\\u1ed3ng n\\u1ed3i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l&agrave;m t\\u1eeb h\\u1ee3p kim nh&ocirc;m cao c\\u1ea5p v\\u1edbi l\\u1edbp ch\\u1ed1ng d&iacute;nh b&ecirc;n trong, c&oacute; \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n cao, an to&agrave;n cho s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi gi&uacute;p cho th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n kh&ocirc;ng b\\u1ecb d&iacute;nh, d\\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng v\\u1ec7 sinh, b\\u1ea3o qu\\u1ea3n. V\\u1ecf n\\u1ed3i b\\u1eb1ng inox s&aacute;ng b&oacute;ng sang tr\\u1ecdng, b\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u1eb9p theo th\\u1eddi gian, t&ocirc; \\u0111i\\u1ec3m cho kh&ocirc;ng gian b\\u1ebfp th&ecirc;m \\u0111\\u1eb9p, hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i. Thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf an to&agrave;n, ti\\u1ec7n l\\u1ee3i, d\\u1ec5 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. N\\u1ed3i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang b\\u1ecb 7 ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 an to&agrave;n nh\\u1eb1m \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o &aacute;p su\\u1ea5t v&agrave; ngu\\u1ed3n \\u0111i\\u1ec7n lu&ocirc;n \\u1edf m\\u1ee9c \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh nh\\u1ea5t. Van \\u0111i\\u1ec1u &aacute;p t\\u1ea1o s\\u1ef1 c&acirc;n b\\u1eb1ng cho &aacute;p su\\u1ea5t v&agrave; gi&uacute;p qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh x\\u1ea3 h\\u01a1i di\\u1ec5n ra nhanh h\\u01a1n. B\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ec9 c\\u1ea7n ch\\u1ecdn ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 n\\u1ea5u v&agrave; th\\u1eddi gian n