ph&uacute;t \\u0111\\u1ebfn 8 gi\\u1edd, t&ugrave;y thu\\u1ed9c v&agrave;o l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng th\\u1ecbt b\\u1ea1n mu\\u1ed1n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Trung b&igrave;nh c\\u1ee9 1kg th\\u1ecbt b\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd ng&acirc;m trong m\\u1ed9t gi\\u1edd. L\\u01b0u &yacute;, b\\u1ea1n n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng gi\\u1ea5y th\\u1ea5m kh&ocirc; th\\u1ecbt tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi chi&ecirc;n, ngo&agrave;i ra \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi c&aacute;nh g&agrave; b\\u1ea1n n&ecirc;n t&iacute;nh th\\u1eddi gian cho kh\\u1ed1i l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng trung b&igrave;nh c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t c&aacute;i nh&eacute;.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><img alt=\\\"B\\u00ed m\\u1eadt n\\u1ea5u n\\u01b0\\u1edbng c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ea7u b\\u1ebfp chuy\\u00ean nghi\\u1ec7p (P1)\\\" data-original=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tgdd.vn\\/Files\\/2017\\/12\\/25\\/1053070\\/bi-mat-nau-nuong-cua-dau-bep-chuyen-nghiep-p1-2_800x450.jpg\\\" data-src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tgdd.vn\\/Files\\/2017\\/12\\/25\\/1053070\\/bi-mat-nau-nuong-cua-dau-bep-chuyen-nghiep-p1-2_800x450.jpg\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tgdd.vn\\/Files\\/2017\\/12\\/25\\/1053070\\/bi-mat-nau-nuong-cua-dau-bep-chuyen-nghiep-p1-2_800x450.jpg\\\" title=\\\"B\\u00ed m\\u1eadt n\\u1ea5u n\\u01b0\\u1edbng c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ea7u b\\u1ebfp chuy\\u00ean nghi\\u1ec7p (P1)\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>3. T\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 th\\u01a1m c\\u1ee7a ti&ecirc;u<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Rang ti&ecirc;u tr&ecirc;n l\\u1eeda cho \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi c&oacute; m&ugrave;i th\\u01a1m r\\u1ed3i cho v&agrave;o c\\u1ed1i gi&atilde;. C&aacute;ch n&agrave;y s\\u1ebd gi&uacute;p h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v\\u1ecb c\\u1ee7a ti&ecirc;u \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph&aacute;t huy t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n trong m&oacute;n \\u0103n c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><img alt=\\\"B\\u00ed m\\u1eadt n\\u1ea5u n\\u01b0\\u1edbng c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ea7u b\\u1ebfp chuy\\u00ean nghi\\u1ec7p (P1)\\\" data-original=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tgdd.vn\\/Files\\/2017\\/12\\/25\\/1053070\\/bi-mat-nau-nuong-cua-dau-bep-c