('97e3ea52-27a3-4f61-977c-c2f31d9eb713', 'en', '6 TUYT CHIU V SINH NH BP HIU QU', '6 TUYT CHIU V SINH NH BP HIU QU', ' v sinh bn ra bt v cng n gin, bn ch cn s dng ming ra chn chi bn trong bn ra vi x phng v nc nng. ng qun chi c vi nc, bn nn dng mt chic bn chi  d dng chi cc ngc ngch, nn dng cng vi dung dch x phng  chi.', '<h3><b>1. V sinh bn ra b&aacute;t nhanh nh&oacute;ng:</b></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; v sinh bn ra b&aacute;t v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng n gin, bn ch cn s dng ming ra ch&eacute;n ch&ugrave;i b&ecirc;n trong bn ra vi x&agrave; ph&ograve;ng v&agrave; nc n&oacute;ng. ng qu&ecirc;n ch&ugrave;i c v&ograve;i nc, bn n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng mt chic b&agrave;n chi  d d&agrave;ng ch&ugrave;i c&aacute;c ng&oacute;c ng&aacute;ch, n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng c&ugrave;ng vi dung dch x&agrave; ph&ograve;ng  ch&ugrave;i.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Nu trong bn xut hin nhng vt r s&eacute;t,  v&agrave;ng kh&oacute; ch&ugrave;i ra th&igrave; bn n&ecirc;n s dng baking soda, chanh, mui hoc mt s loi h&oacute;a cht ty ra du m chuy&ecirc;n dng cho vic<b>&nbsp;v sinh nh&agrave; bp</b>p.</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"Ve_Sinh_Bep_Dien_Bep_Ga\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><b>2. V sinh bp in, bp ga:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;i vi vic v sinh bp in v&agrave; bp ga u kh&aacute; tng t nhau, bn cn dn sch c&aacute;c loi thc n ri v&atilde;i tr&ecirc;n bp, sau o ch cn s dng khn lau  nh&uacute;ng vi dung dch ch&ugrave;i ra  ch&ugrave;i c&aacute;c vt du m b&aacute;m tr&ecirc;n b mt. N&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c loi dung dch ch&ugrave;i ra chuy&ecirc;n dng kh&ocirc;ng cha x&agrave; ph&ograve;ng hay amoniac l&agrave;m n m&ograve;n nh hng n tui th ca bp. i vi c&aacute;c vt bn cng u, ngi d&ugrave;ng n&ecirc;n ch mt thi gian  h&oacute;a cht t&aacute;c dng v&agrave; ty sch vt bn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"Ve_Sinh_Tu_Lanh_Hieu_Qua\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><b>3. V sinh t lnh hiu qu:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;T lnh l&agrave; ni ct gi ch yu c&aacute;c loi thc phm trong gia &igrave;nh, ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; vy ni &acirc;y s cha rt nhiu loi vi khun v&agrave; m&ugrave;i kh&oacute; chu,  m bo t lnh lu&ocirc;n c sch s n&ecirc;n ch&ugrave;i ra t lnh h&agrave;ng tun.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Trc khi tin h&agrave;nh v sinh t lnh, bn n&ecirc;n th&aacute;o in v&agrave; em to&agrave;n b nhng  n trong t lnh b ra ngo&agrave;i  thun tin cho vic ch&ugrave;i ra. D&ugrave;ng gi lau hoc ming bt bin nh&uacute;ng vi dung dch x&agrave; ph&ograve;ng lau sch b mt t lnh, sau &oacute; d&ugrave;ng mt ming gi kh&aacute;c lau sch li vi nc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Mo v sinh nh bp nhanh v hiu qu\" data-filename=\"huong-dan-cach-ve-sinh-nha-bep-3.jpg\" src=\"https://fact-depot.com/media/page/211/Meo-ve-sinh-nha-bep-nhanh-va-hieu-qua%20(1).jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"Ve_Sinh_Tu_Va_Be_Mat_Tu_Bep_Cuc_Nhanh\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><b>4. V sinh t v&agrave; b mt t bp cc nhanh:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;i vi t bp thng cha c&aacute;c loi thc phm kh&ocirc;,  d&ugrave;ng nh&agrave; bp,... bn b&ecirc;n d&agrave;nh gii gian  dn dp mi tun, bi &acirc;y l&agrave; ni a th&iacute;ch ca c&aacute;c lo&agrave;i kin, gi&aacute;n, chut. B mt b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i ca t s d d&iacute;nh c&aacute;c vt du m trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh nu nng, n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c loi khn t c&oacute; thm dung dch ty ra chuy&ecirc;n dng c bit vi c&aacute;c loi t g.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mt bp n&ecirc;n v sinh sau mi ln nu nng  m bo t&iacute;nh v sinh cng nh thm m cho cn bp ca bn. Bn c&oacute; th d d&agrave;ng s dng c&aacute;c loi nc lau bp, c&aacute;c loi&nbsp;<b>h&oacute;a cht ty ra du m</b>&nbsp;a dng tr&ecirc;n th trng. Ngo&agrave;i ra bn cng n&ecirc;n s dng c&aacute;c loi nc xt thm  em li m&ugrave;i hng d chu cho cn bp ca gia &igrave;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"Ve_Sinh_Lo_Vi_Song\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><b>5. V sinh l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;N&ecirc;n th&aacute;o v nng ng&acirc;m vi hn hp nc m c&ugrave;ng x&agrave; ph&ograve;ng,  trong v&agrave;i gi s gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c vt du m b&aacute;m tr&ecirc;n v nng c bong ra mt c&aacute;ch d d&agrave;ng. Khi ch&ugrave;i l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c h&oacute;a cht ty ra du m m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng g&acirc;y n m&ograve;n kim loi. Ngo&agrave;i ra bn cng c&oacute; th d&ugrave;ng hn hp mui v&agrave; baking soda nhng cn che c&aacute;c b phn kim loi  kh&ocirc;ng b n m&ograve;n bi hn hp n&agrave;y. Bn cng n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng th&ecirc;m c&aacute;c h&oacute;a cht kh m&ugrave;i, s&aacute;t khun  m bo l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng lu&ocirc;n sch s nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Mo v sinh nh bp nhanh v hiu qu\" data-filename=\"7d611e13794789705.jpg\" src=\"https://fact-depot.com/media/page/211/Meo-ve-sinh-nha-bep-nhanh-va-hieu-qua%20(2).jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"Ve_Sinh_San_Nha_Bep_Hieu_Qua_Nhanh_Chong\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><b>6. V sinh s&agrave;n nh&agrave; bp hiu qu, nhanh ch&oacute;ng:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Nu &atilde; n&oacute;i n vic v sinh nh&agrave; bp th&igrave; chc chn c&ocirc;ng vic cui c&ugrave;ng trong c&ocirc;ng cuc n&agrave;y &oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; l&agrave;m sch s&agrave;n nh&agrave; bp,  s&agrave;n nh&agrave; bp lu&ocirc;n c sch s th&igrave; ch&uacute;ng ta n&ecirc;n lau s&agrave;n nh&agrave; bp mi ng&agrave;y, va gi&uacute;p sch s li tr&aacute;nh c vic t&eacute; ng&atilde; do c&aacute;c loi du m trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh nu n g&acirc;y ra.  vic l&agrave;m sch s&agrave;n nh&agrave; bp hiu qu, bn c&oacute; th t&igrave;m mua c&aacute;c loi nc lau s&agrave;n s&aacute;t khun trung t&iacute;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Vic&nbsp;<b>v sinh nh&agrave; bp</b>&nbsp;n&oacute;i chung v&agrave; c th l&agrave; l&agrave;m sch c&aacute;c b phn nh t lnh, l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng, s&agrave;n nh&agrave; bp, bn ra b&aacute;t, ...n&oacute;i ri&ecirc;ng l&agrave; vic l&agrave;m rt quan trng  gi cho cn bp lu&ocirc;n sch s v&agrave; tho&aacute;ng m&aacute;t. &quot;Nh&agrave; sch th&igrave; m&aacute;t - b&aacute;t sch ngon cm&quot; mt cn bp sch s em li nhng ba n ngon cho gia &igrave;nh cung cp dinh dng v&agrave; ngn nga bnh bng nhng thc n tt cho sc kho. Fact-Depot hiu c iu n&agrave;y n&ecirc;n &atilde; v&agrave; ang n lc ph&acirc;n phi c&aacute;c sn phm h&aacute;o cht v sinh nh&agrave; bp chnh h&agrave;ng thuc nhiu thng hiu ni ting tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n th gii.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<a fb:like:layout=\"button_count\"><iframe allow=\"encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" data-testid=\"fb:like Facebook Social Plugin\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"25px\" name=\"fbfda0ab2b2c2\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/v2.12/plugins/like.php?action=like&amp;app_id=&amp;channel=https%3A%2F%2Fstaticxx.facebook.com%2Fx%2Fconnect%2Fxd_arbiter%2F%3Fversion%3D46%23cb%3Df34c30f8b5f9ddc%26domain%3Dchienlaishop.vn%26is_canvas%3Dfalse%26origin%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fchienlaishop.vn%252Ff3c3a649b9e028%26relation%3Dparent.parent&amp;container_width=0&amp;font=arial&amp;height=25&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fchienlaishop.vn%2Fnhieu-tinh-keo-dai-thoi-gian-gian-cach-theo-chi-thi-16-cp-672201628956569&amp;layout=button_count&amp;locale=vi_VN&amp;sdk=joey&amp;send=false&amp;share=false&amp;show_faces=false&amp;width=90\" title=\"fb:like Facebook Social Plugin\" width=\"90px\"></iframe></a><br />\r\n<a fb:share:layout=\"button_count\"> </a>'),
('97e3ea52-27a3-4f61-977c-c2f31d9eb713', 'vi', '6 TUYT CHIU V SINH NH BP HIU QU', '6 TUYT CHIU V SINH NH BP HIU QU', ' v sinh bn ra bt v cng n gin, bn ch cn s dng ming ra chn chi bn trong bn ra vi x phng v nc nng. ng qun chi c vi nc, bn nn dng mt chic bn chi  d dng chi cc ngc ngch, nn dng cng vi dung dch x phng  chi.', '<h3><b>1. V sinh bn ra b&aacute;t nhanh nh&oacute;ng:</b></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; v sinh bn ra b&aacute;t v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng n gin, bn ch cn s dng ming ra ch&eacute;n ch&ugrave;i b&ecirc;n trong bn ra vi x&agrave; ph&ograve;ng v&agrave; nc n&oacute;ng. ng qu&ecirc;n ch&ugrave;i c v&ograve;i nc, bn n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng mt chic b&agrave;n chi  d d&agrave;ng ch&ugrave;i c&aacute;c ng&oacute;c ng&aacute;ch, n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng c&ugrave;ng vi dung dch x&agrave; ph&ograve;ng  ch&ugrave;i.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Nu trong bn xut hin nhng vt r s&eacute;t,  v&agrave;ng kh&oacute; ch&ugrave;i ra th&igrave; bn n&ecirc;n s dng baking soda, chanh, mui hoc mt s loi h&oacute;a cht ty ra du m chuy&ecirc;n dng cho vic<b>&nbsp;v sinh nh&agrave; bp</b>p.</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"Ve_Sinh_Bep_Dien_Bep_Ga\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><b>2. V sinh bp in, bp ga:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;i vi vic v sinh bp in v&agrave; bp ga u kh&aacute; tng t nhau, bn cn dn sch c&aacute;c loi thc n ri v&atilde;i tr&ecirc;n bp, sau o ch cn s dng khn lau  nh&uacute;ng vi dung dch ch&ugrave;i ra  ch&ugrave;i c&aacute;c vt du m b&aacute;m tr&ecirc;n b mt. N&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c loi dung dch ch&ugrave;i ra chuy&ecirc;n dng kh&ocirc;ng cha x&agrave; ph&ograve;ng hay amoniac l&agrave;m n m&ograve;n nh hng n tui th ca bp. i vi c&aacute;c vt bn cng u, ngi d&ugrave;ng n&ecirc;n ch mt thi gian  h&oacute;a cht t&aacute;c dng v&agrave; ty sch vt bn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"Ve_Sinh_Tu_Lanh_Hieu_Qua\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><b>3. V sinh t lnh hiu qu:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;T lnh l&agrave; ni ct gi ch yu c&aacute;c loi thc phm trong gia &igrave;nh, ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; vy ni &acirc;y s cha rt nhiu loi vi khun v&agrave; m&ugrave;i kh&oacute; chu,  m bo t lnh lu&ocirc;n c sch s n&ecirc;n ch&ugrave;i ra t lnh h&agrave;ng tun.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Trc khi tin h&agrave;nh v sinh t lnh, bn n&ecirc;n th&aacute;o in v&agrave; em to&agrave;n b nhng  n trong t lnh b ra ngo&agrave;i  thun tin cho vic ch&ugrave;i ra. D&ugrave;ng gi lau hoc ming bt bin nh&uacute;ng vi dung dch x&agrave; ph&ograve;ng lau sch b mt t lnh, sau &oacute; d&ugrave;ng mt ming gi kh&aacute;c lau sch li vi nc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Mo v sinh nh bp nhanh v hiu qu\" data-filename=\"huong-dan-cach-ve-sinh-nha-bep-3.jpg\" src=\"https://fact-depot.com/media/page/211/Meo-ve-sinh-nha-bep-nhanh-va-hieu-qua%20(1).jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"Ve_Sinh_Tu_Va_Be_Mat_Tu_Bep_Cuc_Nhanh\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><b>4. V sinh t v&agrave; b mt t bp cc nhanh:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;i vi t bp thng cha c&aacute;c loi thc phm kh&ocirc;,  d&ugrave;ng nh&agrave; bp,... bn b&ecirc;n d&agrave;nh gii gian  dn dp mi tun, bi &acirc;y l&agrave; ni a th&iacute;ch ca c&aacute;c lo&agrave;i kin, gi&aacute;n, chut. B mt b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i ca t s d d&iacute;nh c&aacute;c vt du m trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh nu nng, n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c loi khn t c&oacute; thm dung dch ty ra chuy&ecirc;n dng c bit vi c&aacute;c loi t g.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mt bp n&ecirc;n v sinh sau mi ln nu nng  m bo t&iacute;nh v sinh cng nh thm m cho cn bp ca bn. Bn c&oacute; th d d&agrave;ng s dng c&aacute;c loi nc lau bp, c&aacute;c loi&nbsp;<b>h&oacute;a cht ty ra du m</b>&nbsp;a dng tr&ecirc;n th trng. Ngo&agrave;i ra bn cng n&ecirc;n s dng c&aacute;c loi nc xt thm  em li m&ugrave;i hng d chu cho cn bp ca gia &igrave;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"Ve_Sinh_Lo_Vi_Song\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><b>5. V sinh l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;N&ecirc;n th&aacute;o v nng ng&acirc;m vi hn hp nc m c&ugrave;ng x&agrave; ph&ograve;ng,  trong v&agrave;i gi s gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c vt du m b&aacute;m tr&ecirc;n v nng c bong ra mt c&aacute;ch d d&agrave;ng. Khi ch&ugrave;i l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c h&oacute;a cht ty ra du m m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng g&acirc;y n m&ograve;n kim loi. Ngo&agrave;i ra bn cng c&oacute; th d&ugrave;ng hn hp mui v&agrave; baking soda nhng cn che c&aacute;c b phn kim loi  kh&ocirc;ng b n m&ograve;n bi hn hp n&agrave;y. Bn cng n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng th&ecirc;m c&aacute;c h&oacute;a cht kh m&ugrave;i, s&aacute;t khun  m bo l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng lu&ocirc;n sch s nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Mo v sinh nh bp nhanh v hiu qu\" data-filename=\"7d611e13794789705.jpg\" src=\"https://fact-depot.com/media/page/211/Meo-ve-sinh-nha-bep-nhanh-va-hieu-qua%20(2).jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"Ve_Sinh_San_Nha_Bep_Hieu_Qua_Nhanh_Chong\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><b>6. V sinh s&agrave;n nh&agrave; bp hiu qu, nhanh ch&oacute;ng:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Nu &atilde; n&oacute;i n vic v sinh nh&agrave; bp th&igrave; chc chn c&ocirc;ng vic cui c&ugrave;ng trong c&ocirc;ng cuc n&agrave;y &oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; l&agrave;m sch s&agrave;n nh&agrave; bp,  s&agrave;n nh&agrave; bp lu&ocirc;n c sch s th&igrave; ch&uacute;ng ta n&ecirc;n lau s&agrave;n nh&agrave; bp mi ng&agrave;y, va gi&uacute;p sch s li tr&aacute;nh c vic t&eacute; ng&atilde; do c&aacute;c loi du m trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh nu n g&acirc;y ra.  vic l&agrave;m sch s&agrave;n nh&agrave; bp hiu qu, bn c&oacute; th t&igrave;m mua c&aacute;c loi nc lau s&agrave;n s&aacute;t khun trung t&iacute;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Vic&nbsp;<b>v sinh nh&agrave; bp</b>&nbsp;n&oacute;i chung v&agrave; c th l&agrave; l&agrave;m sch c&aacute;c b phn nh t lnh, l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng, s&agrave;n nh&agrave; bp, bn ra b&aacute;t, ...n&oacute;i ri&ecirc;ng l&agrave; vic l&agrave;m rt quan trng  gi cho cn bp lu&ocirc;n sch s v&agrave; tho&aacute;ng m&aacute;t. &quot;Nh&agrave; sch th&igrave; m&aacute;t - b&aacute;t sch ngon cm&quot; mt cn bp sch s em li nhng ba n ngon cho gia &igrave;nh cung cp dinh dng v&agrave; ngn nga bnh bng nhng thc n tt cho sc kho. Fact-Depot hiu c iu n&agrave;y n&ecirc;n &atilde; v&agrave; ang n lc ph&acirc;n phi c&aacute;c sn phm h&aacute;o cht v sinh nh&agrave; bp chnh h&agrave;ng thuc nhiu thng hiu ni ting tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n th gii.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a fb:share:layout=\"button_count\"> </a>'),
('97e3ead7-e45b-446e-a3ad-18e7c80cd785', 'en', '7 MN NGON N BT NG LM T L VI SNG CC N GIN', '7 MN NGON N BT NG LM T L VI SNG CC N GIN', 'Vi mn n ny, bn cn s dng l vi sng c chc nng nng. Bn ct tht heo thnh ming nh va n. Sau , p tht heo vi cc gia v: mt ong, ng v hng, du ho, hnh ti', '<h3><strong>1. Tht heo nng xi&ecirc;n rau c</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Tht xin nng bng l vi sng \" data-xsrc=\"/Data/image/2017/09/15/mon-ngon-lam-tu-lo-vi-song-thit-xien.jpg\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://s.meta.com.vn/img/thumb.ashx/Data/image/2017/09/15/mon-ngon-lam-tu-lo-vi-song-thit-xien.jpg\" title=\"Tht xin nng bng l vi sng \" width=\"700\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tht xi&ecirc;n nng bng l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vi m&oacute;n n n&agrave;y, bn cn s dng l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng c&oacute; chc nng nng. Bn ct tht heo th&agrave;nh ming nh va n. Sau &oacute;, p tht heo vi c&aacute;c gia v: mt ong, ng v hng, du h&agrave;o, h&agrave;nh ti,... Tht p xong, xi&ecirc;n th&agrave;nh tng que (xi&ecirc;n xen k tht v&agrave; t &agrave; Lt v&agrave;o que). Cho tht v&agrave;o l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng, bt ch  nng trong 10 ph&uacute;t cho tht ch&iacute;n u. B tht ra a v&agrave; thng thc.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>2. G&agrave; nng mt ong</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"G nng mt ong vi l vi sng \" data-xsrc=\"/Data/image/2017/09/15/mon-ngon-lam-tu-lo-vi-song-ga-nuong.jpg\" height=\"535\" src=\"https://s.meta.com.vn/img/thumb.ashx/Data/image/2017/09/15/mon-ngon-lam-tu-lo-vi-song-ga-nuong.jpg\" title=\"G nng mt ong vi l vi sng \" width=\"750\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>G&agrave; nng mt ong vi l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bn p g&agrave; vi nc st gm:&nbsp;ti gi&atilde; nhuyn, s xay nh, t th&aacute;i nh, ng, ng v hng, du n, nc mm... p g&agrave; vi nc st tr&ecirc;n trong 3 - 4 ting cho tht thm u.&nbsp;Cho g&agrave; &atilde; tm p gia v v&agrave;o khay nng &atilde; l&oacute;t giy nn, sau &oacute; d&ugrave;ng chi qu&eacute;t u mt ong l&ecirc;n m&igrave;nh g&agrave;. S dng l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng c&oacute; ch  nng. Nng g&agrave;  nhit  200  C&nbsp;trong khong 20 ph&uacute;t, ri chuyn ch  la tr&ecirc;n, thoa u mt ong l&ecirc;n m&igrave;nh g&agrave; ln na.&nbsp;Khong 2 ph&uacute;t th&igrave; lt g&agrave; cho ti khi g&agrave; ch&iacute;n s c&oacute; m&agrave;u v&agrave;ng. Sau &oacute;, bn c&oacute; th b&agrave;y tht g&agrave; ra a  thng thc.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>3. Tht b&ograve; kh&ocirc;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\" Sy tht b kh bng l vi sng\" data-xsrc=\"/Data/image/2017/09/15/mon-ngon-lam-tu-lo-vi-song-thit-bo-kho.jpg\" height=\"508\" src=\"https://s.meta.com.vn/img/thumb.ashx/Data/image/2017/09/15/mon-ngon-lam-tu-lo-vi-song-thit-bo-kho.jpg\" title=\" Sy tht b kh bng l vi sng\" width=\"750\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Sy tht b&ograve; kh&ocirc; bng l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tht b&ograve; ra sch, ct mng, p vi ti, s, t, ng, mm, du h&agrave;o, ng v hng... un tht b&ograve; tr&ecirc;n bp nh la, y vung khong 25 ph&uacute;t n khi tht chuyn sang m&agrave;u n&acirc;u. Khi tht ngui, d&ugrave;ng c&aacute;n dao gin cho tht mm. Lu &yacute; kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave;m n&aacute;t tht. Sau &oacute; xe nh va n. Cho tht v&agrave;o l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng khong 110  C  sy, t ch  hn gi c 10 ph&uacute;t bn o tht 1 ln n khi n&agrave;o t  kh&ocirc; mong mun. Thi gian sy mt khong 30 ph&uacute;t.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>4. B&aacute;nh Flan</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\" Lm bnh Flan vi l vi sng\" data-xsrc=\"/Data/image/2017/09/15/mon-ngon-lam-tu-lo-vi-song-banh-flan.jpg\" height=\"438\" src=\"https://s.meta.com.vn/img/thumb.ashx/Data/image/2017/09/15/mon-ngon-lam-tu-lo-vi-song-banh-flan.jpg\" title=\" Lm bnh Flan vi l vi sng\" width=\"700\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;L&agrave;m b&aacute;nh Flan vi l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bn l&agrave;m caramen bng c&aacute;ch cho 1/2 mung c&agrave; ph&ecirc; ng v&agrave;o cc c&ugrave;ng mt mung canh nc lc. Cho v&agrave;o l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng vn  c&ocirc;ng sut cao trong 5 ph&uacute;t. Ht thi gian ly cc ra l&uacute;c n&agrave;y ng &atilde; chuyn sang m&agrave;u v&agrave;ng n&acirc;u.&nbsp;Pha sa ti v&agrave;o sa c, khuy u, cho v&agrave;o l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng vn n&uacute;t c&ocirc;ng sut cao trong 5 ph&uacute;t. Trng &aacute;nh u, lc r&acirc;y ri  v&agrave;o hn hp tr&ecirc;n. Cho hn hp trng sa v&agrave;o cc caramen,  trong l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng  c&ocirc;ng sut trung b&igrave;nh thp trong v&ograve;ng 9 ph&uacute;t.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>5. C&aacute; hp</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\" Mn c hp bng l vi sng\" data-xsrc=\"/Data/image/2017/09/15/mon-ngon-lam-tu-lo-vi-song-ca-hap.jpg\" height=\"678\" src=\"https://s.meta.com.vn/img/thumb.ashx/Data/image/2017/09/15/mon-ngon-lam-tu-lo-vi-song-ca-hap.jpg\" title=\" Mn c hp bng l vi sng\" width=\"750\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;M&oacute;n c&aacute; hp bng l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ra sch, ct c&aacute; th&agrave;nh tng kh&uacute;c nh. p vi ng, du h&agrave;o, x&igrave; du v&agrave; gng th&aacute;i si trong 10 ph&uacute;t.&nbsp;Sau &oacute;, cho a c&aacute; v&agrave;o l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng, bt l&ograve;  ch  nu khong 6 ph&uacute;t. Sau 6 ph&uacute;t bn  nguy&ecirc;n a c&aacute; trong l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng, cho c&aacute; t ht nhit bt trong khong 5 ph&uacute;t ri bt ch  nu th&ecirc;m khong 4 ph&uacute;t na cho c&aacute; ch&iacute;n. Sau &oacute;, bn c&oacute; th b c&aacute; ra thng thc. C&aacute; va ch&iacute;n ti s va mm va ngt rt hp dn.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>6. Trng hp</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\" Trng hp l vi sng\" data-xsrc=\"/Data/image/2017/09/15/mon-ngon-lam-tu-lo-vi-song-trung-hap.jpg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.meta.com.vn/img/thumb.ashx/Data/image/2017/09/15/mon-ngon-lam-tu-lo-vi-song-trung-hap.jpg\" title=\" Trng hp l vi sng\" width=\"540\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Trng hp l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trng &aacute;nh u, n&ecirc;m gia v va n, b v&agrave;o 1 ch&eacute;n nh, nh y np. Cho v&agrave;o l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng, bt c&ocirc;ng sut cao trong v&ograve;ng 2 ph&uacute;t, th&agrave;nh phm s c mt a trng hp ngon l&agrave;nh, b&ocirc;ng xp. Bn c&oacute; th trang tr&iacute; bng h&agrave;nh l&aacute; th&aacute;i nh ph&iacute;a tr&ecirc;n cho p mt v&agrave; th&ecirc;m hng v.</p>'),
