('987e6e5d-e32e-4417-84a1-a08dc06966e9', 'vi', 'Galaxy Z Fold 3 v Z Flip 3 s c gi r hn', 'Galaxy Z Fold 3 v Z Flip 3 s c gi r hn', 'Hai smartphone t nht ca Samsung s c gi r hn 400 USD so vi th h trc.', '<p>Hai smartphone t nht ca Samsung s c&oacute; gi&aacute; r hn 400 USD so vi th h trc.</p>\r\n\r\n<article>\r\n<p>Theo b&aacute;o c&aacute;o ca&nbsp;<em>SamMobile</em>&nbsp;nhm ph bin smartphone m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh gp cng nh ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh mc ti&ecirc;u 7 triu m&aacute;y ca hai model khi ra mt,&nbsp;Galaxy Z Fold 3&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;Galaxy Z Flip 3&nbsp;s r hn 20% so&nbsp;Z Fold 2&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;Z Flip. Theo &oacute;, Galaxy Z Fold 3 s c&oacute; gi&aacute; 1.599 USD v&agrave; Z Flip 3 l&agrave; 959 USD.</p>\r\n\r\n<figure data-size=\"true\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"><img alt=\"Samsung ang dn u th trng v smartphone mn hnh gp. nh:Phonearena.\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" data-src=\"https://i1-sohoa.vnecdn.net/2021/06/08/insider-hints-at-likely-samsun-1694-1549-1623088597.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=bYAMpJ-8yHbcRV_gkntPng\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" itemprop=\"contentUrl\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i1-sohoa.vnecdn.net/2021/06/08/insider-hints-at-likely-samsun-1694-1549-1623088597.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=bYAMpJ-8yHbcRV_gkntPng\" />\r\n<figcaption itemprop=\"description\">\r\n<p>Samsung ang dn u th trng v smartphone m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh gp. nh:&nbsp;<em>Phonearena.</em></p>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<p>Hai model n&agrave;y s c trang b chip x l&yacute; mi nht ca&nbsp;Qualcomm&nbsp;- Snapdragon 888. Z Flip 3 cha c&oacute; th&ocirc;ng tin v cu h&igrave;nh, c&ograve;n Z Fold 3 s c trang b 12 GB RAM v&agrave; b nh trong 256 GB.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Z Fold 3 c&oacute; m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh ngo&agrave;i 6,21 inch, m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh trong nh hn so vi th h trc, c&ograve;n 7,55 inch. M&aacute;y s c&oacute; pin 4.380 mAh, h tr sc nhanh 25W. M&aacute;y chy&nbsp;Android 11&nbsp;khi ra mt v&agrave; s c n&acirc;ng cp l&ecirc;n&nbsp;Android&nbsp;th h mi trong 3 nm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Z Flip3 s c trang b m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh ch&iacute;nh 6,9 inch, tc  l&agrave;m ti 120 Hz v&agrave; c&oacute; vin mng c&ugrave;ng camera trc dng c l nh hn. M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i cng tng k&iacute;ch thc. i k&egrave;m l&agrave; pin 3.900 mAh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu nm nay&nbsp;Samsung&nbsp;khai t d&ograve;ng Galaxy Note, Z Fold 3 s c h tr S Pen v&agrave; b&uacute;t n&agrave;y s t&iacute;ch hp trong m&aacute;y. H&atilde;ng cng s s dng k&iacute;nh si&ecirc;u mng UTG th h th hai vi  bn cao hn cho Z Fold 3.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Z Flip 3 s s dng cm camera ging&nbsp;Galaxy S21, vi camera ch&iacute;nh v&agrave; camera g&oacute;c si&ecirc;u rng 12 megapixel, camera tele 64 megapixel vi kh nng zoom hybrid 3x. Galaxy Z Fold 3 c&oacute; th trang b camera ging&nbsp;S21 Ultra. Ngo&agrave;i ra, model n&agrave;y cng c trang b camera n di m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo&nbsp;<em>Ice Universe</em>, s kin Unpacked ca Samsung c&oacute; th din ra v&agrave;o gia hoc cui th&aacute;ng 6. Hai model Galaxy Z Fold 3 v&agrave; Z Flip 3 s c giao n kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng trong th&aacute;ng 7.</p>\r\n</article>');
