('97e1f7ee-29ba-470d-bc86-9fcaa3e91a33', 'vi', 'Gi Massage Hng Ngoi 8 bi Cao Cp Chnh Hng', 'Gi Massage Hng Ngoi 8 bi Cao Cp Chnh Hng', 'Gi massage hng ngoi 8 bi c ai d dng mc vo lng ta ca gh ngi vn phng hoc gh xe hi', '<h2><strong>Gi Massage Hng Ngoi Cao Cp Ch&iacute;nh H&atilde;ng</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Thit k gn, nh tin li mang theo di chuyn d d&agrave;ng, kh&ocirc;ng chim din t&iacute;ch ct gi, h&igrave;nh d&aacute;ng chic gi n&ecirc;n rt thun tin massage s dng nhiu v tr&iacute; tr&ecirc;n ngi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cht liu ca gi vi lp da v&agrave; li tho&aacute;ng kh&iacute; bc ngo&agrave;i, c&oacute;  &agrave;n hi tt, mm mi, an to&agrave;n d chu khi tip x&uacute;c vi b mt da, c bit lp li gi&uacute;p bn c&oacute; cm gi&aacute;c thoi m&aacute;i kh&ocirc;ng b b&iacute; b&aacute;ch kh&oacute; chu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"gi massage hng ngoi cao cp\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" src=\"../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/goi-massage-hong-ngoai.jpg\" srcset=\"https://sgshop.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/goi-massage-hong-ngoai.jpg 800w, https://sgshop.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/goi-massage-hong-ngoai-300x300.jpg 300w, https://sgshop.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/goi-massage-hong-ngoai-150x150.jpg 150w, https://sgshop.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/goi-massage-hong-ngoai-768x768.jpg 768w, https://sgshop.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/goi-massage-hong-ngoai-600x600.jpg 600w, https://sgshop.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/goi-massage-hong-ngoai-100x100.jpg 100w\" width=\"800\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gi massage Magic PL 818 vi thit k t&acirc;n tin 8 bi c&oacute; kh nng xoay 360  massage chuy&ecirc;n s&acirc;u.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>T&iacute;nh nng nhit hng ngoi gi&uacute;p l&agrave;m n&oacute;ng nhanh v&ugrave;ng m&aacute;t xa, chuy&ecirc;n nghip nh 1 k thut vi&ecirc;n tht th.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>U IM NI BT</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Gi massage hng ngoi 8 bi c&oacute; ai d d&agrave;ng mc v&agrave;o lng ta ca gh ngi vn ph&ograve;ng hoc gh xe hi. S dng gi massage sau nhiu gi lin l&agrave;m vic mt mi li&ecirc;n tc trc m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&aacute;y vi t&iacute;nh, hoc tr&ecirc;n ngi tr&ecirc;n xe &ocirc;t&ocirc; l&acirc;u s em n cm gi&aacute;c d chu, th gi&atilde;n nht.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gi massage hng ngoi 8 bi c thit k gn nh v&agrave; sang trng, va s dng va  trang tr&iacute;  vn ph&ograve;ng, ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch, xe hi&hellip; V&agrave; d d&agrave;ng mang theo c&ugrave;ng bn khi i picnic, du lch hay i c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c xa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Vi 3 ch  massage kh&aacute;c nhau:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Gi massage hng ngoi\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" src=\"../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/goi-massage-hong-ngoai-3.jpg\" srcset=\"https://sgshop.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/goi-massage-hong-ngoai-3.jpg 800w, https://sgshop.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/goi-massage-hong-ngoai-3-300x300.jpg 300w, https://sgshop.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/goi-massage-hong-ngoai-3-150x150.jpg 150w, https://sgshop.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/goi-massage-hong-ngoai-3-768x768.jpg 768w, https://sgshop.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/goi-massage-hong-ngoai-3-600x600.jpg 600w, https://sgshop.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/goi-massage-hong-ngoai-3-100x100.jpg 100w\" width=\"800\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Massage thng:  ch  n&agrave;y c&aacute;c &egrave;n ni vi&ecirc;n bi massage tt, s dng  massage nhc mi th&ocirc;ng thng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Massage Hng Ngoi (N&oacute;ng):  ch  n&agrave;y c&aacute;c &egrave;n ni vi&ecirc;n bi massage s&aacute;ng l&ecirc;n, s dng massage th&ecirc;m nhit khi thi tit lnh hoc l&agrave; khi s dng chung vi c&aacute;c thuc xoa b&oacute;p. Vi t&aacute;c dng massage v&agrave; l&agrave;m m thuc s c&oacute; t&aacute;c dng hn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Massage b&igrave;nh thng 2 ph&uacute;t (2 v&ograve;ng), ri chuyn sang massage hng ngoi 2 ph&uacute;t (2 v&ograve;ng) s &aacute;nh tan nhc mi v&agra