ttps://sgshop.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/noi-ap-xuat-asanzo-nap-roi-100x100.jpg 100w\" width=\"800\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vi c&ocirc;ng ngh nu k&iacute;n hi gi&uacute;p thc n nhanh ch&iacute;n,tit kim in n 30% Sn phm gim thi gian nu n 15%, thi gian nu ch&aacute;o v&agrave; s&uacute;p n 40%. Thc n nu ch&iacute;n nhanh nhng vn gi nguy&ecirc;n m&ugrave;i v, cht dinh dng. C&oacute; chc nng hn gi tin li gi&uacute;p bn c&oacute; th l&agrave;m vic kh&aacute;c hoc ngh ngi th gian trong khi ni ang nu m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng lo thc n s b ch&aacute;y, kh&ocirc;ng ch&iacute;n,&hellip; Ni c&oacute; thit b bo v 7 lp m bo an to&agrave;n cho ngi s dng. Sn phm a nng, c&oacute; th d&ugrave;ng nu cm, ch&aacute;o, canh, hm, hp thc n&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ni &aacute;p sut a nng Asanzo PC-65AS1 c&oacute; dung t&iacute;ch 6 L, gi&uacute;p bn thoi m&aacute;i ch bin c&aacute;c m&oacute;n n ngon cho gia &igrave;nh. L&ograve;ng ni bng hp kim nh&ocirc;m tr&aacute;ng men chng d&iacute;nh, v ni bng inox cao cp gi&uacute;p ngi s dng s th&ecirc;m tin li, nhanh ch&oacute;ng khi ch bin c&aacute;c m&oacute;n n thm ngon cho gia &igrave;nh. Sn phm c&oacute; nhiu chc nng nh: nu cm, nu ch&aacute;o, nu canh, nu soup, hm thc n&hellip; Nu thc n nhanh ch&iacute;n, gi nguy&ecirc;n hng v, cht dinh dng. Ni c&oacute; c&ocirc;ng sut 1.000W v&agrave; np y k&iacute;n, kh&iacute;t cht gi cho hi kh&ocirc;ng tho&aacute;t ra ngo&agrave;i. Nh vy m&agrave; &aacute;p sut v&agrave; nhit  trong ni tng cao, gi&uacute;p thc n nhanh ch&iacute;n m&agrave; vn gi c nguy&ecirc;n vn m&ugrave;i v v&agrave; c&aacute;c cht dinh dng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ni &aacute;p sut a nng Asanzo PC-65AS1 cht liu nh&ocirc;m cao cp, chng d&iacute;nh. Lng ni c l&agrave;m t hp kim nh&ocirc;m cao cp vi lp chng d&iacute;nh b&ecirc;n trong, c&oacute;  bn cao, an to&agrave;n cho sc khe ng thi gi&uacute;p cho thc n kh&ocirc;ng b d&iacute;nh, d d&agrave;ng v sinh, bo qun. V ni bng inox s&aacute;ng b&oacute;ng sang trng, bn p theo thi gian, t&ocirc; im cho kh&ocirc;ng gian bp th&ecirc;m p, hin i. Thit k an to&agrave;n, tin li, d s dng. Ni c trang b 7 chc nng bo v an to&agrave;n nhm m bo &aacute;p sut v&agrave; ngun in lu&ocirc;n  mc n nh nht. Van iu &aacute;p to s c&acirc;n bng cho &aacute;p sut v&agrave; gi&uacute;p qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh x hi din ra nhanh hn. Bn ch cn chn ch  nu v&agrave; thi gian nu ph&ugrave; hp vi tng m&oacute;n n, trong khi ni ang nu, bn vn c&oacute; th l&agrave;m nhng c&ocirc;ng vic kh&aacute;c.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Lu &yacute; khi s dng ni &aacute;p sut:</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; i vi thc n c&oacute;  n cao v&agrave; sinh bt nh ch&aacute;o, u, lng thc phm gii hn l&agrave; 2/3 dung t&iacute;ch ni.<br />\r\n&ndash; i vi c&aacute;c thc n kh&aacute;c (tht, c&aacute;) lng thc phm gii hn kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; 3/4 dung t&iacute;ch ni.<br />\r\n&ndash; Trc khi s dng, phi y np k, vn np &uacute;ng chiu  &oacute;ng tht k&iacute;n, kim tra li c&aacute;c van  tr&aacute;nh b nght van.<br />\r\n&ndash; Ch&uacute; &yacute; thi gian nu v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng  cn nc, dn n ch&aacute;y hng ni. Khi cn bn n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng ng h hn gi  nhc nh thi gian.<br />\r\n&ndash; V sinh ni &aacute;p sut sau khi s dng, lau ch&ugrave;i k roan, th&ocirc;ng van thng xuy&ecirc;n, kh&ocirc;ng  thc n, bi bn l&agrave;m tc van, g&acirc;y b&iacute;t l x&igrave; hi, d dn n ch&aacute;y n.</p>'),
('987e636b-cbbf-4ec1-be65-996e4025adc0', 'vi', 'Samsung Galaxy Note 21', 'Samsung Galaxy Note 21', 'Tit kim: 1.500.000 so vi gi th trng', '<p>Samsung l&agrave; mt trong nhng nh&agrave; sn xut dn u tr&ecirc;n th trng in thoi th&ocirc;ng minh nhiu nm qua. Sau th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng ca d&ograve;ng Galaxy S20 series, Samsung &atilde; tr li v&agrave; tip tc khng nh v th cho d&ograve;ng flagship cao cp ca m&igrave;nh. D&ograve;ng Galaxy S21 series &aacute;nh du bc nhy vt vi nhng c&ocirc;ng ngh ti&ecirc;n tin nht hin nay. &aacute;ng ch&uacute; &yacute;, Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bn u ti&ecirc;n v&agrave; duy nht trong d&ograve;ng sn phm nm nay c t&iacute;ch hp c&ugrave;ng b&uacute;t S Pen. &ldquo;T&acirc;n binh khng long&rdquo; n&agrave;y ha hn s dn u xu hng v&agrave; to ra nhng tri nghim ng cp, kh&aacute;c bit cho ngi d&ugrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://hoanghamobile.com/Uploads/2021/01/16/s21-ultra.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thit k nguy&ecirc;n bn camera lin cnh ng cp</p>\r\n\r\n<p>in thoi Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng dn u cho xu hng thit k mi, kh&aacute;c bit ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n so vi nhng smartphone hin nay. Cm camera nguy&ecirc;n khi c gn lin vi cnh v&agrave; khung kim loi ca m&aacute;y, mang li cm gi&aacute;c nam t&iacute;nh hn v&agrave; v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng tinh xo. in thoi c&ograve;n c trang b mt lp k&iacute;nh Corning&reg; Gorilla&reg; Glass Victus bn b nht hin nay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://hoanghamobile.com/Uploads/2021/01/16/s21-ultra-2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng s hu m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh AMOLED 2X 6.8 inch vi tn s qu&eacute;t t 10Hz - 120Hz mt m&agrave;. Nh &oacute;, in thoi c&oacute; th mang n tri nghim h&igrave;nh nh sng ng, sc n&eacute;t n tng chi tit nhng vn tit kim thi lng pin &aacute;ng k. Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G cung cp h&igrave;nh nh s&aacute;ng hn 25%, ti a 1.500nits so vi th h c. C&ugrave;ng vi t l tng phn ci thin 50% cho hin th r&otilde; n&eacute;t bt chp mi iu kin. Nh&agrave; sn xut cng b sung t&iacute;nh nng Eye Comfort Shield hn ch ti a t&igrave;nh trng mi mt khi s dng li&ecirc;n tc. M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh ca Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G t tin em n cho ngi d&ugrave;ng tri nghim a t&aacute;c v t hc tp, l&agrave;m vic n gii tr&iacute; kh&ocirc;ng gii hn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&ocirc;ng ngh camera vt tri nht t Samsung</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kh&ocirc;ng ch c&oacute; thit k b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i ng cp, chic Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng c&ograve;n s hu h thng camera ti&ecirc;n tin nht hin nay. M&ocirc;-un camera h&igrave;nh ch nht cha bn cm bin vi mt ng k&iacute;nh ch&iacute;nh 108MP. Ngo&agrave;i ra c&ograve;n c&oacute; mt camera g&oacute;c si&ecirc;u rng 12MP, camera tele si&ecirc;u rng 10MP v&agrave; camera tele k&eacute;p 10MP. H thng camera n&agrave;y h tr chp nh HDR 12 bit vi m&agrave;u sc phong ph&uacute; hn 64 ln v&agrave; di ng rng hn ba ln.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://hoanghamobile.com/Uploads/2021/01/16/s21-ultra-3.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng c&ograve;n h tr thu ph&oacute;ng chun kh&ocirc;ng gian 100X, mt ng k&iacute;nh zoom quang hc 3X v&agrave; mt ng k&iacute;nh zoom quang hc 10X. Bn thm ch&iacute; c&oacute; th to ra nhng thc phim chuy&ecirc;n nghip vi t&iacute;nh nng quay video 4K  tc  60 khung h&igrave;nh/gi&acirc;y. Cm bin chp &ecirc;m &atilde; c ci tin  gim nhiu v&agrave; bt c nhiu &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng hn. C&ocirc;ng ngh Nona-binning 12MP c kt hp mang n nhng bc nh sc n&eacute;t vi cht lng tuyt vi. Ngo&agrave;i ra, n&oacute; c&ograve;n c&oacute; mt camera selfie 40MP  ho&agrave;n thin tri nghim chp h&igrave;nh cho ngi d&ugrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kt ni cc nhanh, tng th&iacute;ch cc nh vi S Pen</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bn duy nht trong 3 bin th tng th&iacute;ch vi b&uacute;t S Pen ti&ecirc;u chun. N&oacute; c&oacute; th h tr c&aacute;c tri nghim t v, ghi ch&uacute;, chnh sa h&igrave;nh nh n chp nh selfie ch vi thao t&aacute;c cc n gin. Nh c&ocirc;ng ngh t Wacom, ngi d&ugrave;ng c&oacute; th tri nghim b&uacute;t S Pen y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch ngay tr&ecirc;n chic Galaxy S21 Ultra n&agrave;y. Kh&aacute;c vi Galaxy Note, chic Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; khe cm ri&ecirc;ng cho b&uacute;t S Pen. Thay v&agrave;o &oacute; bn c&oacute; th mua ng chic b&uacute;t S Pen trong mt cover b&aacute;n c&ugrave;ng m&aacute;y v&agrave; ly ra s dng rt d d&agrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://hoanghamobile.com/Uploads/2021/01/16/s21-ultra-4.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhng nm qua, Samsung vn ang n lc nghi&ecirc;n cu  ph&aacute;t trin tc  kt ni tr&ecirc;n nhng chic smartphone ca m&igrave;nh. Samsung Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G t h&agrave;o l&agrave; mt trong nhng in thoi th&ocirc;ng minh u ti&ecirc;n h tr Wi-Fi 6E. Nh c cung cp nhiu bng th&ocirc;ng hn, kt ni Internet tr&ecirc;n chic smartphone n&agrave;y nhanh hn gp 4 ln, ngi d&ugrave;ng c&oacute; th chia s c&aacute;c ni dung ch trong nh&aacute;y mt. So vi d&ograve;ng Galaxy S20 series, kt ni mng 5G tr&ecirc;n Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G &atilde; c ci thin &aacute;ng k. N&oacute; &atilde; gim  tr kt ni xung mc thp nht, cho ngi d&ugrave;ng tri nghim trc tuyn mt m&agrave; hn. in thoi Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G c trang b con chip Exynos 2100 5nm mnh m v&agrave; tit kim nng lng hn. N&oacute; cng i k&egrave;m vi vi&ecirc;n pin 5000mAh c&oacute; th sc y 50% ch trong 30 ph&uacute;t.</p>'),
('987e64f5-d25b-4c17-bd21-2fc0bdb96bcc', 'vi', 'Apple iPhone 12 Mini New', 'Apple iPhone 12 Mini New', 'Thng hiu: Apple M sn phm: ipmax-1s', '<p>Tt c iPhone ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng VN/A c ph&acirc;n phi ti Poco Mart&nbsp;u c nhp trc tip t C&ocirc;ng ty TNHH Apple Vit Nam. Poco Mart l&agrave; nh&agrave; b&aacute;n l y quyn ch&iacute;nh thc ca Apple ti Vit Nam.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://hoanghamobile.com/Uploads/Content/2020/10/14/apple--dien-thoai-di-dong-apple-iphone-12-mini-64gb-chinh-hang-vn-a-1.JPG\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tem ICT c&oacute; tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c sn phm iPhone ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng VN/A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mua iPhone 12 gi&aacute; r ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng ti Poco Mart</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 13/10 va qua, Apple &atilde; ch&iacute;nh thc cho ra mt th h iPhone 12 mi vi 4 phi&ecirc;n bn, v&agrave; trong &oacute; mu iPhone 12 ti&ecirc;u chun, vi nhiu ci tin v c b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i ln b&ecirc;n trong, ha hn s li tip tc ni tip s th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng t chic iPhone 11 tin nhim.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thit k c l&agrave;m mi li ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhc ti Apple, ngi d&ugrave;ng s lu&ocirc;n ngh ti nhng thit b iPhone ng cp, mang tr&ecirc;n m&igrave;nh mt thit k v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng sang trng, hin i v&agrave; thi thng. V&agrave; iPhone 12 Series ca nm nay cng kh&ocirc;ng phi l&agrave; mt ngoi l. Mu iPhone 12 64GB s hu mt thit k &atilde; c &ldquo;lt x&aacute;c&rdquo; ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n so vi c&aacute;c th h tin nhim trc &acirc;y vi cnh c v&aacute;t phng, vu&ocirc;ng th&agrave;nh sc cnh, mang ti mt cm gi&aacute;c cc k&igrave; bn b v&agrave; chc chn. Thit k n&agrave;y khin cho ngi d&ugrave;ng c&oacute; th d d&agrave;ng li&ecirc;n tng ti nhng mu iPhone huyn thoi trc &acirc;y &atilde; l&agrave;m n&ecirc;n t&ecirc;n tui ca Apple nh iPhone 4 hoc iPhone 5.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"maxresdefault-177\" src=\"https://hoanghamobile.com/Uploads/Content/2020/10/14/apple--dien-thoai-di-dong-apple-iphone-12-128gb-chinh-hang-vn-a-2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh ca iPhone 12 64GB c trang b c&ocirc;ng ngh tm nn OLED Super Retina XDR, mang li cho iPhone 12 mt cht lng hin th xut sc nht t trc n nay. i c&ugrave;ng vi &oacute; l&agrave;  ph&acirc;n gii Full HD 2,532 x 1,170; cho mt  im nh cc tt l&ecirc;n ti 460ppi. Vi m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh c n&acirc;ng cp v&agrave; ci tin nh vy, nhng v ch nh&acirc;n s hu iPhone 12 c&oacute; th thoi m&aacute;i thng thc nhng b phim hoc chi game m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn phi lo ngh v bt c iu g&igrave;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&ldquo;Qu&aacute;i th&uacute; hiu nng&rdquo; vi b vi x l&yacute; Apple A14 Bionic</p>\r\n\r\n<p>S hu mt v b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i sang trng, b&oacute;ng by v&agrave; lch l&atilde;m l&agrave; vy, th nhng iPhone 12 64GB li mang trong m&igrave;nh mt sc mnh cc k&igrave; khng khip, vt tri hn tt c nhng mu smartphone ang c&oacute; mt tr&ecirc;n th trng. Tt c l&agrave; nh c&oacute; b vi x l&yacute; Apple A14 Bionic c sn xut tr&ecirc;n tin tr&igrave;nh 5nm mi nht, kh&ocirc;ng ch manh m&agrave; c&ograve;n tit kim in nng ti ti a. Con chip n&agrave;y c &aacute;nh gi&aacute; l&agrave; b vi x l&yacute; mnh m nht, nhanh nht hin nay vi cu to t 6 l&otilde;i CPU, 11,8 t b&oacute;ng b&aacute;n dn, 4 l&otilde;i GPU mi, v&agrave; nhanh hn A13 Bionic ti 40%. C&ocirc;ng ngh kt ni mng 5G mi c&ugrave;ng vi Wi-Fi 6 cng &atilde; c a v&agrave;o iPhone 12, ha hn s mang ti mt kh nng kt ni Internet vt tri ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"lcimg-a62d96d8-e998-4803-9ac5-dce77df28439\" src=\"https://hoanghamobile.com/Uploads/Content/2020/10/14/apple--dien-thoai-di-dong-apple-iphone-12-128gb-chinh-hang-vn-a-3.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>c bit, tr&iacute; tu nh&acirc;n to AI Neural Engine gi &acirc;y cng &atilde; c n&acirc;ng l&ecirc;n th&agrave;nh 16 l&otilde;i, v&igrave; vy n&ecirc;n vi x l&yacute; Apple A14 Bionic c&oacute; th t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n c 11 ngh&igrave;n t ph&eacute;p t&iacute;nh trong mt gi&acirc;y. B nh 